title: ToastedspikesLWT
author: orikebise
pages:
#- My Last Will and Testament
By Toastedspikes
Dear traveller. I hope you found this book well I have travelled far and wide, yet I could not find my destination I ended up here, in this wild jungle, creepers everywhere. I
#- don't have long to write this, but take heed I cannot go on. I can't it's hopeless I'll leave my possessions, what little I have, here Perhaps I can start anew? I will do what it takes, I shan't go on with my life anymore. Maybe you, traveller, might
#- find a use for my belongings. Goodbye, Toastedspikes, former resident of Black Cat Commune.
#- This Bookworm book has been transfered to Minecraft book and quill by Librarian Orikebise, of the Agora State University, March 26th, 2013
#- 